text: Florent Massip (born 29 March 1994) is a French rugby union full-back and he currently plays for Provence Rugby in the French Pro D2 . ==References== ==External links== *Provence profile *L'Équipe profile Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:French people of Réunionnais descent Category:French rugby union players Category:Rugby union fullbacks Category:Provence Rugby players Category:Black French sportspeople
